snippet.title: FIFA 17 - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Official FIFA 17 gameplay trailer featuring James Rodriguez, Eden Hazard, Marco Reus and Anthony Martial. See the new features: http://x.ea.com/6777

FIFA 17 completely innovates in the way players think and move, physically interact with opponents, and execute in attack, putting you in control of every moment on the pitch.

See FIFA 17's new mode Powered by Frostbite  - The Journey http://x.ea.com/6779

Become an EA SPORTS FIFA Insider and get the latest FIFA 17 news via email: http://x.ea.com/6778

Pre-order for extra FIFA Ultimate Team content: http://x.ea.com/6782 

FIFA 17 is available globally from September 29 on Xbox One, Xbox 360, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 3 and PC.

Subscribe for more FIFA 17 gameplay videos: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD

MUSIC: "Chariots" by Paper Route (facebook.com/paperroute)
iTunes: http://flyt.it/chariotsiTunes
Apple Music: http://flyt.it/chariotsApple
Spotify: http://flyt.it/PaperRouteSpotify
